00:15:12,800 --> 00:15:14,080
Miss Biyu,

192
00:15:14,920 --> 00:15:15,800
this golden hair stick

193
00:15:18,160 --> 00:15:19,920
was put in that cellar

194
00:15:21,000 --> 00:15:24,040
