195
00:15:26,600 --> 00:15:27,480
Miss Biyu,

196
00:15:28,960 --> 00:15:29,880
are you aware that

197
00:15:30,280 --> 00:15:31,680
though this scheme is ingenious,

198
00:15:32,560 --> 00:15:35,600
