235
00:17:07,160 --> 00:17:07,920
I don't know.

236
00:17:15,120 --> 00:17:16,520
All gangs in the city

237
00:17:16,520 --> 00:17:17,800
took the Anhua

238
00:17:18,120 --> 00:17:19,680
